{"tid":962630,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"無啦無啦... 樓價指數按月跌3.5%跌幅擴大","createTime":"2018-12-31T04:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T14:45:29.000Z","uid":28245,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1b77ee02f24c2494c5c4c8dda094d54c0b09fc","tid":962630,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"差餉物業估價署公布，最新11月份私樓樓價指數報366.3點，按月跌13.3點，跌幅擴大至3.5%，連跌4個月，累積跌幅7.2%，指數重返今年2月水平。<br />\n<br />\n指數顯示，最新報366.3點，按月跌幅為3.5%，較之前一個月的跌幅2.57%，進一步擴大，較7月份時歷史高位394.8點，連跌4個月，累積挫7.2%，回到今年2月份364.5點相近水平。<br />\n<br />\n若以5類單位面積劃分，各類單位樓價指數全數下跌。當中以中小型單位跌幅較明顯，A類約430平方呎以下按月跌幅3.67%，而B類431至752平方呎單位跌幅更大，最新報348.2點，接月跌3.76%。中大型單位單位按月跌幅則介乎1.4%至2.1%不等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個月跌3.5% <br />\n440萬計 一個月無左15萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c893bf9b2fb3a1d35ca3ae10603cae1ad77484b","tid":962630,"uid":112720,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"自住驚閪喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c48293129118b1594a8834aef62bee7f5f0586","tid":962630,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"没事儿"},{"pid":"fb955d0289e25def3508ffe94b40d39a0e07b0af","tid":962630,"uid":216432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"保升保平安"},{"pid":"95027b3077810ed7f72707a7c6f12bd05a5b2bae","tid":962630,"uid":107927,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"跌35%先開始驚啦"},{"pid":"e695438e537a6e606cf1422da05612604276f7e9","tid":962630,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"保升中心升左一萬呀<br />\n<br />\n3zero個乞衣劏房升左九成呀<br />\n<br />\n租租慢慢租啦"},{"pid":"b11b3133744d35e90b475dc575e16155b963198c","tid":962630,"uid":78791,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"907aab8eaeda69e